Try it and thank me later! These muffins are packed with protein and are super easy to make.

Ingredients:
  • Oats (using @pintola.in High protein Oats here)
  • 1 ripped banana
  • 1 whole egg
  • 1 cup milk
  • 1 tsp baking powder
  • 1 scoop whey (chocolate flavour)
  • Dark chocolate chips (optional but recommended!)

1. Mix all ingredients in a bowl until smooth.
2. Pour into muffin tins and bake for 15–20 mins.
3. Let them cool (if you can wait) and enjoy!

(High protein dessert, protein muffins, no oil muffins, oats muffin, healthy desserts)
